    "en": {
      "title": "4.4 million are registered for the National Fuel License",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Electricity and Energy, 4.4 million people have registered for the National Fuel License. The minister also said that this system has been tested in 536 fuel stations of Cipetco (442) and IOC (94) today.",
        "The Minister says that 1807005 transactions have taken place and the amount of fuel issued is 1477622 liters."
      ],
